## Examples

| Script | Description |
|---|---|
| `examples/basic_simulation.py` | Single step stimulus, default parameters |
| `examples/pulse_train_stimulation.py` | Repetitive pulse train with depleting reserve pool |

---

## Physical model overview

```
Electrical stimulus I_ext(t)
        │
        ▼
┌───────────────────────┐
│  Membrane (HH + LCa)  │  C_m dV/dt = I_ext − I_Na − I_K − I_Ca − I_L
│  gate vars: m,h,n,d,f │
└───────────┬───────────┘
            │ I_Ca (L-type)
            ▼
┌───────────────────────┐
│  Calcium dynamics     │  d[Ca]/dt = −α·I_Ca − ([Ca]−[Ca]_rest)/τ_Ca
└───────────┬───────────┘
            │ [Ca²⁺]
            ▼
┌───────────────────────┐
│  Exocytosis model     │  k_exo([Ca]) — Hill / allosteric
└───────────┬───────────┘
            │ k_exo
            ▼
┌───────────────────────┐
│  Vesicle pool kinetics│  Reserve → Docked ──k_exo──▶ Released
└───────────────────────┘
```

