## Units

| Quantity | Unit |
|---|---|
| Voltage | mV |
| Time | ms |
| Current density | µA/cm² |
| Conductance density | mS/cm² |
| Capacitance | µF/cm² |
| Ca²⁺ concentration | µM |
| Vesicle counts | dimensionless |

